ðŸ“Š Next.js Performance Optimization Guide & Tracking Notes

  • Core Web Vitals: LCP < 2.5s, FID < 100ms, CLS < 0.1 for good user experience
  • Next.js Specific Optimizations: Use Image component, dynamic imports, API routes optimization
  • Bundle Analysis: Run `npm run build` and analyze bundle sizes regularly
  • Tailwind Purging: Ensure unused CSS is purged in production builds
  • Static Generation: Use getStaticProps/getServerSideProps appropriately
  • Image Optimization: Implement Next.js Image component with proper sizing
  • Code Splitting: Use dynamic imports and lazy loading for heavy components
  • Caching Strategy: Implement proper cache headers and CDN usage
  • Mobile First: 60%+ traffic is mobile, prioritize mobile performance
  • Monitoring Tools: Vercel Analytics, Google PageSpeed, Lighthouse CI, Web Vitals
